          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".A strong anticorrelation between fluctuation of nu",
                " and E-gamma for 1+ resonances has been found.",
                " A result which is attributed to the role of the",
                " (n,gamma F) reaction.",
                ".For overlapping resonances, uncorrected and corrected",
                " values are given where it was possible to make the",
                " correction.",
                "** By compilers: private communication to NNDC from",
                "   Soleihac treats nu-p=2.874 at En=246.6 keV",
                "   instead of 346.6 keV (from 22592 where data for",
                "   239Pu were received in private comm. to NNDC,",
                "   from Soleilhac, 1976/3/10.)"
              ]
            }
          ],
